	<h1 class="title">世界上最会赚钱的女歌手说，她是穿着H&amp;M长大的</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/26306/small/26306.jpg?1455710291" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">宣海伦 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-27 08:52:19 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18135/medium/18135.png?1448545158" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="18135" data-title="《世界上最会赚钱的女歌手说，她是穿着H&amp;M长大的》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/18135/medium/18135.png?1448545158" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/18135.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
